detail_desc: Calf-length dress in a crêpe weave with a round neckline and a small opening with a button at the back of the neck. Short sleeves with a flounce over each shoulder and covered elastication at the hems. Gathered seams on the skirt for added width. Unlined.

Calf-length dress in a crêpe weave with a round neckline and a small opening with a button at the back of the neck. Short sleeves with a flounce over each shoulder and covered elastication at the hems. Gathered seams on the skirt for added width. Unlined.
Short dress in a viscose weave with a visible seam centre back, long sleeves with a zip at the cuffs, and a rounded hem.

Calf-length dress in a crêpe weave with short, elasticated, frill-trimmed sleeves and flounces down the front. Opening with buttons at the back, a smocked seam at the waist and slit at the front. Unlined. The polyester content of the dress is partly recycled.

Wide, straight-cut, calf-length dress in soft, gently draping satin with a sheen. V-neck and a yoke on the shoulders and at the back. Long, gathered, voluminous balloon sleeves with a seam at the top and close-fitting cuffs with a covered button. Short slits in the sides.
Fitted top in softly draping, fine-ribbed jersey made from a silk blend with extra-long sleeves. Ribbing around the neckline and raw edges at the cuffs and hem.
Joggers in lightweight sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with covered elastication and a drawstring at the waist. Tapered legs with jersey ribbing at the hems.
Fitted sports vest tops in fast-drying functional fabric with a racer back.
5-pocket shorts in cotton denim in a relaxed fit with a regular waist, button fly, low crotch and straight, wide legs.
Fitted top in soft, ribbed viscose jersey with a turtle neck and long sleeves.
Mesh shorts with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets.
Sun visor in fabric and transparent, tinted plastic with a mesh sweatband and elastication at the back.
Socks in a soft rib knit with elasticated, frill-trimmed tops.
Socks in a soft, jacquard-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.
